      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>to the pan, give everything a good mix up then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and top the sauce with the <strong>haddock bites</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
